name: Elon&Trump
description: The Elon-Trump Coin ($ENT) is a unique cryptocurrency that combines the world of memes and blockchain innovation. It leverages the influence of two iconic figures, Elon Musk and Donald Trump, to create a dynamic token ecosystem where value is influenced by real-world events. Designed for entertainment and utility, $ENT supports meme creators, rewards community engagement, and drives decentralized creativity.
